00:44:04.640 --> 00:44:06.890
[heroic music]

795
00:44:08.560 --> 00:44:10.890
[grunts aggressively]

796
00:44:11.600 --> 00:44:13.150
[man grunts in pain]

797
00:44:13.270 --> 00:44:14.860
[bone crunches]

798
00:44:17.360 --> 00:44:18.570
